precis:
Amendment to the CANADIAN WHEAT BOARD REGULATIONS establishing higher
initial payments for the base grades of wheat (increase of $8 to $109 per
tonne), amber durum wheat (increase of $8 to $98 per tonne) and barley
(increase of $10 to $86 per tonne) for the 1991/92 crop year.
